job.title: NHM Staff Nurse Recruitment 2021  Apply Online for 2624 vacancies in Madhya Pradesh
job.body:
Total Vacancies: 2624

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Contractual Staff Nurse 

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for Nurses has been published by National Health Mission for Staff Nurse vacancies in Madhya Pradesh. If you are searching for a government job in Madhya Pradesh then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of ANM from 01-06-2021, and till 22-06-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Madhya Pradesh. and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about application fee

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Staff Nurse in NHM, your GNM, B.Sc (Nursing) must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is the 01-06-2021
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 22-06-2021 

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 40 years old. 

NHM Staff Nurse Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is

as per norms

How to apply for NHM Staff Nurse Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Staff Nurse. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of NHM and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by NHM
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
